DONE
	*	Support all Verbs: GET, PUT, POST, DELETE
	* Use Generics to return typed results
	* Support JSON using SuperObject

Requirements
	* Support HTTPS
	* Result should supports Xml
	* Must provide support to Delphi 7
	* Transparent serialization/desserialization in delphi side. 
	* Support marshaller plugins for custom formats
	* URIBuilder to construct with support to:
		-	Addressable with QueryParams: servername/controllername/actionname?par1&par2
		- Addressable with URI params: servername/controllername/actionname/par1/par2
	* Can also use anonymous methods to register callback of requests
	* Integrable into Rest DataSnap
	* Support DBXJson to delphi 2010 and up.